# Livewire UI — Convenciones SistemasEscolares

> **Ver también**: reglas 031 (Design System), 032 (Navegación), 033 (Accesibilidad), 035 (Validación)

## Estructura de un componente CRUD estándar

```php
namespace App\Livewire\Core;

use Livewire\Component;
use Livewire\WithPagination;
use Livewire\Attributes\Validate;
use App\Models\Core\Terlec;

class TerlecIndex extends Component
{
    use WithPagination;

    public string $search = '';
    public bool   $showForm = false;
    public ?int   $editId = null;
    public ?int   $confirmDeleteId = null;

    #[Validate('required|integer|min:1990|max:2100')]
    public ?int $ano = null;

    #[Validate('required|integer|min:0')]
    public ?int $orden = null;

    public function updatedAno(): void  { $this->validateOnly('ano'); }
    public function updatedOrden(): void { $this->validateOnly('orden'); }

    public function crear(): void
    {
        $this->reset(['editId', 'ano', 'orden']);
        $this->orden   = (int)(Terlec::max('orden') ?? 0) + 1;
        $this->showForm = true;
    }

    public function editar(int $id): void
    {
        $item = Terlec::findOrFail($id);
        $this->editId = $id;
        $this->ano    = $item->ano;
        $this->orden  = $item->orden;
        $this->showForm = true;
    }

    public function guardar(): void
    {
        $this->validate();
        // crear/actualizar...
        $this->dispatch('toast', message: 'Guardado correctamente.', type: 'success');
        $this->cancelar();
    }

    public function confirmarBorrar(int $id): void { $this->confirmDeleteId = $id; }

    public function borrar(): void
    {
        Terlec::findOrFail($this->confirmDeleteId)->delete();
        $this->dispatch('toast', message: 'Eliminado.', type: 'success');
        $this->cancelar();
    }

    public function cancelar(): void
    {
        $this->reset(['showForm', 'editId', 'ano', 'orden', 'confirmDeleteId']);
        $this->resetValidation();
    }

    public function render()
    {
        return view('livewire.core.terlec.index', [
            'terlecs' => Terlec::orderBy('orden')->get(),
        ]);
    }
}
```

## Estructura de vista Blade estándar

```blade
<div>
    {{-- 1. Page header con breadcrumbs y acción primaria --}}
    <x-ui.page-header title="Ciclos lectivos" :breadcrumbs="[…]">
        <x-slot:actions>
            <x-ui.button wire:click="crear" icon="plus">Nuevo</x-ui.button>
        </x-slot:actions>
    </x-ui.page-header>

    {{-- 2. Flash messages --}}
    @if(session('success')) <x-ui.alert variant="success" class="mb-4">…</x-ui.alert> @endif

    {{-- 3. Formulario inline en card (si aplica) --}}
    @if($showForm)
        <x-ui.card class="mb-6">
            <x-slot:title>Nuevo / Editar</x-slot:title>
            <form wire:submit="guardar" class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                <div>
                    <label class="label label-required">Año</label>
                    <input type="number" wire:model.blur="ano"
                           class="input @error('ano') input-error @enderror" />
                    @error('ano') <p class="error-msg">…{{ $message }}</p> @enderror
                </div>
                <div class="col-span-2 flex justify-end gap-3 border-t pt-4">
                    <x-ui.button type="button" variant="ghost" wire:click="cancelar">Cancelar</x-ui.button>
                    <x-ui.button type="submit" variant="primary" icon="check">Guardar</x-ui.button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </x-ui.card>
    @endif

    {{-- 4. Tabla con componentes UI --}}
    <x-ui.table>
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <x-ui.th>Año</x-ui.th>
                <x-ui.th right>Acciones</x-ui.th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody class="divide-y divide-neutral-100">
            @forelse($terlecs as $item)
                <tr class="tr-hover">
                    <x-ui.td>{{ $item->ano }}</x-ui.td>
                    <x-ui.td right>
                        @if($confirmDeleteId == $item->id)
                            <x-ui.button size="sm" variant="danger" wire:click="borrar">Sí</x-ui.button>
                            <x-ui.button size="sm" variant="ghost"  wire:click="cancelar">No</x-ui.button>
                        @else
                            <button class="btn-icon" wire:click="editar({{ $item->id }})">
                                <x-icons.pencil class="w-4 h-4" />
                            </button>
                            <button class="btn-icon-danger" wire:click="confirmarBorrar({{ $item->id }})">
                                <x-icons.trash class="w-4 h-4" />
                            </button>
                        @endif
                    </x-ui.td>
                </tr>
            @empty
                <tr><td colspan="2" class="p-0">
                    <x-ui.empty-state title="Sin registros" message="…" icon="calendar" />
                </td></tr>
            @endforelse
        </tbody>
    </x-ui.table>
</div>
```

## Layouts disponibles

| Layout | Archivo | Uso |
|---|---|---|
| Staff | `layouts.staff` | Gestión (sidebar + topbar) |
| Autogestión | `layouts.autogestion` | Alumnos (mobile-first) |
| Auth | `layouts.auth` | Login pages |

## Reglas de oro

1. **Paleta**: solo tokens `brand.*`, `primary-*`, semánticos. No `indigo-*`, `gray-*` directos.
2. **Componentes**: `<x-ui.button>`, `<x-ui.card>`, `<x-ui.table>`, `<x-ui.alert>`, etc. 
3. **Iconos**: `<x-icons.nombre class="w-4 h-4" />` — Heroicons inline.
4. **Validación**: `#[Validate]` + `validateOnly` en `updated*` + `validate()` en submit.
5. **Mensajes**: `$this->dispatch('toast', message: '...', type: 'success|danger')`.
6. **Navegación**: `wire:navigate` en todos los links internos.
7. **Accesibilidad**: `aria-invalid`, `aria-describedby`, `aria-label` en botones-icono.
